<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.2.10">
<l>cīrār poḻilcūḻn taḻakā yatillait tirucit rakūṭat tuṟaiceṅ kaṇmāluk</l>
<l>kārā tavuḷḷat tavarkēṭ ṭuvappa valainī rulakuk karuḷē puriyum</l>
<l>kārār puyaṟkaik kalikaṉ ṟikuṉṟā volimā laiyoṟoṉ patōṭoṉ ṟumvallār</l>
<l>pārā rulaka maḷantā ṉaṭikkīḻp palakā laniṟkum paṭivāḻ vartāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master the nine-and-one [verses] in a garland</l>
<l rend="indent">of the flawless words of Kalikaṉṟi,</l>
<l>Whose hands are [like] a flood filled by the monsoon</l>
<l rend="indent">which grants grace to the earth with wavy seas,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that those with insatiable hearts delight, hearing [it],</l>
<l>To bright-eyed Māl who dwells in Tiruccitrakūṭam in Tillai</l>
<l rend="indent">that is beautiful [with] fine groves surrounding it,</l>
<l>They will live in [such] a way that [they] stay many times low [at] the feet</l>
<l rend="indent">of him who measured the expanse-filled earth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
